      "id": "chase_vision",
      "text": "Surrender to the excitement",
      "description": "Finally, you have something to reach for.",
      "resultText": "You let the ambition consume you in the best way. Every moment becomes fuel for the dream. You start planning, researching, making connections, taking steps. The energy is electric. Sleep feels optional. The mundane obligations of daily life become obstacles to resent. You're alive with purpose in a way you've never been before. It's intoxicating, and you hope this feeling never ends.",
